data.eml:eml: High diversity of Caligus species (Copepoda: Siphonostomatoida: Caligidae) in Taiwanese waters

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ho, Ju-Shey, Lin, Ching-Long, Liu, Wei-Cheng (2016): High diversity of Caligus species (Copepoda: Siphonostomatoida: Caligidae) in Taiwanese waters. Zootaxa 4174 (1): 114-121, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4174.1.8
